  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is Maya: Cats of Istanbul?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maya: Cats of Istanbul is a hidden object game where you need to find adorable cats hidden in the streets and historical landmarks of Istanbul. As you search for the cats cleverly tucked into intricate details, you will explore Istanbul’s iconic architecture and lose yourself in its detailed models.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/bf728f53515b7472d273808e2665059a.poster.avif?t=1743614957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/bf728f53515b7472d273808e2665059a.webm?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/bf728f53515b7472d273808e2665059a.mp4?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotate the entire city,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/88962338cb42782dc8457d63dd8f2c29.poster.avif?t=1743614957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/88962338cb42782dc8457d63dd8f2c29.webm?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/88962338cb42782dc8457d63dd8f2c29.mp4?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check every tree,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/f8b8de56d4769b891423797b0b7ff9be.poster.avif?t=1743614957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/f8b8de56d4769b891423797b0b7ff9be.webm?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/f8b8de56d4769b891423797b0b7ff9be.mp4?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open every trash box</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/b9934ccb55f64aa6644e2a6de4b3e78a.poster.avif?t=1743614957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/b9934ccb55f64aa6644e2a6de4b3e78a.webm?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/b9934ccb55f64aa6644e2a6de4b3e78a.mp4?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/a2f7749a3886361d479cf0c62261e943.poster.avif?t=1743614957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/a2f7749a3886361d479cf0c62261e943.webm?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413270/extras/a2f7749a3886361d479cf0c62261e943.mp4?t=1743614957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game consists of different levels featuring Istanbul’s iconic locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galata Tower</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hagia Sophia</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Topkapi Palace</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-300 cats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Animated 3D cats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Clickable objects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Relaxing music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Detailed small, cute city models</p>",
